text: Michel Bouquet (born 13 July 1951) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aubervilliers
